    <text>
        <body>
                <div1>
                    <div2>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134a01"/>大魏武定七年歲次己巳四月丙戌朔四月八日癸巳　司州魏郡易陽人今為武安龍山寺主比丘道&CB07018;記
                    </div2>
                    <div2> 
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b01"/>夫萬相具朗。非有非無。是非雙寂。人莫知其元。所以然者。皆由積善空<note n="0134001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30783;＝王【中研院】</note><app n="0134001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">王</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30783;</rdg></app><note n="0134002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02442;＝之【中研院】</note><app n="0134002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02442;</rdg></app>前。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b02"/><note n="0134003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30784;＝苦【中研院】</note><app n="0134003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">苦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30784;</rdg></app>行授記<note n="0134004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02442;＝之【中研院】</note><app n="0134004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02442;</rdg></app>後。便能絜真見樹。定想三九。亦能麾五指以伏狂<note n="0134005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30785;＝象【中研院】</note><app n="0134005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">象</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30785;</rdg></app>。併鬼<note n="0134006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30786;＝王【中研院】</note><app n="0134006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">王</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30786;</rdg></app>於壙
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b03"/>野。把火龍而盤掌。指熾焱而為長流。特挺孤秀。英奇<note n="0134007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30811;＝若【中研院】</note><app n="0134007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">若</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30811;</rdg></app>此。遉顯伏致滅者矣。況 
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b04"/>聚沙<note n="0134008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB15626;＝泡【中研院】</note><app n="0134008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">泡</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB15626;</rdg></app>沫。寧無壞乎。是以此法師。名道諱&CB07018;。迺承波長漢。赤龍之胤。元在河<note n="0134009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">閒＝間【中研院】</note><app n="0134009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">間</lem><rdg wit="【原】">閒</rdg></app>。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b05"/>今寄<note n="0134010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB05464;＝居【中研院】</note><app n="0134010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">居</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB05464;</rdg></app>易陽人也。<note n="0134011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30788;＝棄【中研院】</note><app n="0134011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">棄</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30788;</rdg></app><note n="0134012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30789;＝彼【中研院】</note><app n="0134012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30789;</rdg></app>宮城。割愛辭<note n="0134013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30790;＝親【中研院】</note><app n="0134013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">親</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30790;</rdg></app>。倍加韶響。非情所翫。遂寫素<note n="0134014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30791;＝服【中研院】</note><app n="0134014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">服</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30791;</rdg></app>。懃心道
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b06"/>君。雖同生滅。遠鑒始<note n="0134015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30792;＝終【中研院】</note><app n="0134015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">終</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30792;</rdg></app>。古今競曉。絜行桑門。纖理靡損。持<note n="0134016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13806;＝禁【中研院】</note><app n="0134016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">禁</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13806;</rdg></app>帶浮。罹剎<note n="0134017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30813;＝杜【中研院】</note><app n="0134017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">杜</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30813;</rdg></app>塞。懼
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b07"/>念傷蘭。<note n="0134018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30793;＝斷【中研院】</note><app n="0134018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">斷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30793;</rdg></app><note n="0134019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB03288;＝息【中研院】</note><app n="0134019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">息</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB03288;</rdg></app><note n="0134020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30794;＝繼【中研院】</note><app n="0134020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">繼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30794;</rdg></app>草。清清志絜。春松無以侔其鮮。<note n="0134021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB05471;＝希【中研院】</note><app n="0134021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">希</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB05471;</rdg></app><note n="0134022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB05471;＝希【中研院】</note><app n="0134022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">希</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB05471;</rdg></app>獨<note n="0134023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30795;＝穎【中研院】</note><app n="0134023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">穎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30795;</rdg></app>。夜炬無以匹其照。方
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b08"/>欲<note n="0134024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30814;＝拔【中研院】</note><app n="0134024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">拔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30814;</rdg></app><note n="0134025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30784;＝苦【中研院】</note><app n="0134025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">苦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30784;</rdg></app>窟<note n="0134026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30796;＝宅【中研院】</note><app n="0134026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">宅</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30796;</rdg></app>。雲昇<note n="0134027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30819;＝彼【中研院】</note><app n="0134027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30819;</rdg></app>岸。都不復以世慕為榮也。便率<note n="0134028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30789;＝彼【中研院】</note><app n="0134028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30789;</rdg></app>英傑。信心令&CB02499;一百餘
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b09"/>人。共<note n="0134029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30815;＝裁【中研院】</note><app n="0134029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">裁</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30815;</rdg></app>己貴。同尊上道。且使育王盡藏。須達傾珍。無以比其福。即乃運石荊巖。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b10"/>左置文碑。右法勇塔。雕錯漏彩。連剋聖容之質。狀如真見。晌&CB30782;<note n="0134030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30812;＝若【中研院】</note><app n="0134030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">若</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30812;</rdg></app>丹霞<note n="0134031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30798;＝之【中研院】</note><app n="0134031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30798;</rdg></app>斑。<note n="0134032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30799;＝金【中研院】</note><app n="0134032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30799;</rdg></app>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b11"/>瓔<note n="0134033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30800;＝向【中研院】</note><app n="0134033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">向</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30800;</rdg></app>&CB30823;。如曜靈<note n="0134034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02442;＝之【中研院】</note><app n="0134034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02442;</rdg></app>入魚淵。兼下神蔡。奇章<note n="0134035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30801;＝顯【中研院】</note><app n="0134035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30801;</rdg></app>分。亦<note n="0134036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30802;＝治【中研院】</note><app n="0134036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">治</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30802;</rdg></app>形<note n="0134037" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30803;＝影【中研院】</note><app n="0134037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">影</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30803;</rdg></app>。漢朝感夢。宋君偤勇。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b12"/>陵風拊伏。<note n="0134038" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30797;＝若【中研院】</note><app n="0134038"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">若</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30797;</rdg></app>真鎮神川於中<note n="0134039" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00527;＝庭【中研院】</note><app n="0134039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">庭</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00527;</rdg></app>。顯志長衢。遊人之矚目者也。珞珞<note n="0134040" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30797;＝若【中研院】</note><app n="0134040"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">若</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30797;</rdg></app>七<note n="0134041" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30816;＝星【中研院】</note><app n="0134041"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">星</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30816;</rdg></app><note n="0134042" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02442;＝之【中研院】</note><app n="0134042"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02442;</rdg></app>紀
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b13"/><note n="0134043" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30804;＝天【中研院】</note><app n="0134043"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">天</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30804;</rdg></app>。巖巖如五岳<note n="0134044" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02442;＝之【中研院】</note><app n="0134044"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02442;</rdg></app><note n="0134045" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30805;＝綱【中研院】</note><app n="0134045"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">綱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30805;</rdg></app>地。馨風遐振。<note n="0134046" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB03140;＝璨【中研院】</note><app n="0134046"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">璨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB03140;</rdg></app>爛<note n="0134047" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30394;＝彌【中研院】</note><app n="0134047"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30394;</rdg></app>遠。聲霑北<note n="0134048" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13426;＝海【中研院】</note><app n="0134048"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">海</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13426;</rdg></app>。飛嚮南冥。故為作頌曰。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b14"/><note n="0134049" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB12752;＝彌【中研院】</note><app n="0134049"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB12752;</rdg></app>劫長遠。積善空<note n="0134050" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30786;＝王【中研院】</note><app n="0134050"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">王</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30786;</rdg></app>。行端万有。難比難方。散髮要請。必求所<note n="0134051" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30807;＝長【中研院】</note><app n="0134051"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">長</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30807;</rdg></app>。<note n="0134052" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30784;＝苦【中研院】</note><app n="0134052"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">苦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30784;</rdg></app>行二三。銘記
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b15"/>定光。世雄無匹。廣救一<note n="0134053" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">仞＝切【中研院】</note><app n="0134053"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">切</lem><rdg wit="【原】">仞</rdg></app>。五指現師。狂<note n="0134054" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30785;＝象【中研院】</note><app n="0134054"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">象</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30785;</rdg></app><note n="0134055" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30806;＝乃【中研院】</note><app n="0134055"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">乃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30806;</rdg></app>滯。伏鬼壙野。兩<note n="0134056" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB20010;＝炎【中研院】</note><app n="0134056"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">炎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB20010;</rdg></app>同翳。舍利乃悟。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b16"/>人生得<note n="0134057" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB09497;＝濟【中研院】</note><app n="0134057"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">濟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB09497;</rdg></app>。熾火冰流。咸獲淨地。沙門清潔。規<note n="0134058" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30817;＝矩【中研院】</note><app n="0134058"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">矩</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30817;</rdg></app>古今。守<note n="0134059" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13806;＝禁【中研院】</note><app n="0134059"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">禁</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13806;</rdg></app>持浮。罹剎息心。每懼
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b17"/>傷蘭。結草軀沉。雲昇<note n="0134060" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30819;＝彼【中研院】</note><app n="0134060"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30819;</rdg></app>岸。與聖相尋。率<note n="0134061" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30789;＝彼【中研院】</note><app n="0134061"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30789;</rdg></app>令&CB02499;。裁捨己珍。同尊上道。剋像潛神。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b18"/>育<note n="0134062" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30786;＝王【中研院】</note><app n="0134062"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">王</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30786;</rdg></app>不並。須達豈申。抽靳截骨。早求出因。取石荊丘。雕彩<note n="0134063" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30801;＝顯【中研院】</note><app n="0134063"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30801;</rdg></app>章。<note n="0134064" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30818;＝圖【中研院】</note><app n="0134064"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30818;</rdg></app>形真見。煥如
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b19"/>故常。晌&CB30782;鮮明。<note n="0134065" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30800;＝向【中研院】</note><app n="0134065"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">向</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30800;</rdg></app>&CB30823;雜光。塵驚嚮應。風發鏘鏘。其下神龜。能聖復妖。形<note n="0134066" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30803;＝影【中研院】</note><app n="0134066"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">影</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30803;</rdg></app>漢<note n="0134067" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00527;＝庭【中研院】</note><app n="0134067"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">庭</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00527;</rdg></app>。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0134b20"/>夢感宋朝。置<note n="0134068" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02442;＝之【中研院】</note><app n="0134068"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02442;</rdg></app>神川。宇宙照照。紀<note n="0134069" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30810;＝天【中研院】</note><app n="0134069"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">天</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30810;</rdg></app><note n="0134070" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30805;＝綱【中研院】</note><app n="0134070"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">綱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30805;</rdg></app>地。名遐遠霄。
                    </div2>
